Kru "Ah"

Bandit Leader "Don't tell me you've killed them all..."

Bandit Leader "Really?!"
Kru "But they might die soon... Um, Umi-san?"
Umi "...What?"
Kru "Could you heal a few more of them?"
Umi "Again..."

Afterwards, thanks to Umi's healing magic, the entire band of thieves
managed to cling to life. They cried and apologized to us, adoring Umi by
calling her 'big sis' while they looked at me with fearful eyes.
Well, it can't be helped... they were a step away from death, after all.

By the time we left the thieves' hideout, the day was already turning to
dusk, and it was too late to return to the village.
So we decided to stay in town for another night before departing.
